# Approach
1-> In 1st for loop: we store every character of string in map.
2-> In second for loop: We store key-values in multimap so that values are sorted in ascending order.
3-> Now as our values are sorted we use insert function and this function operates like this-
    it will add `i.second `character `i.first` times in the last of the string res.
4-> As the values are in ascending order so we reverse the resultant string and simply return.

